  "remarks": "Associated with the Islamic International Brigade (IIB) (QDe.099), the\nSpecial Purpose Islamic Regiment (SPIR) (QDe.101) and Emarat Kavkaz (QDe.131). Review\npursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 17 May\n2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 8 November 2022. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
